# Naming Conventions

| Kind | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Types / classes | PascalCase | `UserAccount` |
| Functions / methods | camelCase (JS/TS) / snake_case (Python/Go) | `getUserById` / `get_user_by_id` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `MAX_RETRIES` |
| Files | kebab-case for non-source, language default for source | `api-client.ts` |
| Test files | `<name>.test.<ext>` or `<name>_test.<ext>` | `user.test.ts` |
| Env vars | `PROJECT_FEATURE_VARIABLE` | `MYAPP_DB_URL` |

(Fill in any project-specific deviations above.)
